  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --purple:       #9654C7;
      --purple-mid:   #7B3DAE;
      --purple-light: #F3ECFB;
      --purple-pale:  #FAF5FF;
      --ink:          #1A1A2E;
      --body:         #4A4A5A;
      --white:        #FFFFFF;
      --border:       #E8DCF5;
      --font-display: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
      --font-body:    'Jost', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      color: var(--body);
      background: var(--white);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    /* Nav */
    .nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .nav-inner {
      max-width: 1160px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      height: 72px;
    }

    .nav-logo img { height: 48px; width: auto; }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      list-style: none;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--body);
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--purple); }

    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--purple);
      color: var(--white) !important;
      padding: 0.55rem 1.25rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--purple-mid) !important; }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      max-width: 1160px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 6rem 2rem 5rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-text { max-width: 560px; }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--purple);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .hero-headline {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4.5vw, 3.5rem);
      line-height: 1.15;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    }

    .hero-headline .underline-word {
      position: relative;
      display: inline;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .hero-headline .underline-word::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: -4px;
      height: 4px;
      width: 0;
      background: var(--purple);
      border-radius: 2px;
      animation: drawLine 0.9s ease forwards 0.6s;
    }

    @keyframes drawLine { to { width: 100%; } }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: var(--body);
      margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
    }

    .hero-sub strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--purple);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--purple-mid); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    .btn-ghost {
      color: var(--purple);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      padding: 0.85rem 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--purple);
      transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--purple-mid); border-color: var(--purple-mid); }

    .hero-visual { display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }

    .hero-logo-card {
      background: var(--purple-light);
      border-radius: 2rem;
      padding: 3.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 400px;
    }

    .hero-logo-card img { width: 180px; height: auto; }

    .hero-logo-tagline {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--purple-mid);
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Mission Bar */
    .mission-bar {
      background: var(--purple);
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .mission-bar p {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      color: var(--white);
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* Section Base */
    .section { padding: 5rem 2rem; }

    .section-inner { max-width: 1160px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--purple);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .section-body {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: var(--body);
    }

    .section-body p + p { margin-top: 1.25rem; }

    /* About Connected Speech */
    .about-cs { background: var(--white); }

    .about-cs-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 5rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-cs-visual {
      background: var(--purple-light);
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 3rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 320px;
    }

    .about-cs-visual img { width: 200px; height: auto; opacity: 0.9; }

    .values-list {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .value-item { display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; }

    .value-dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--purple);
      margin-top: 7px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .value-item p { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--body); }

    /* About Jodi */
    .about-jodi { background: var(--purple-pale); }


    .jodi-credentials {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .credential {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--body);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .credential-icon { color: var(--purple); font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 1px; flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* Conditions */
    .conditions { background: var(--white); }

    .conditions-intro { max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

    .conditions-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .condition-card {
      background: var(--purple-pale);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .condition-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(150, 84, 199, 0.12);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .condition-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; display: block; }

    .condition-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .condition-desc { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--body); }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-section { background: var(--purple); padding: 5rem 2rem; text-align: center; }

    .cta-section h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .cta-section p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto 2.25rem;
    }

    .btn-white {
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--purple);
      padding: 0.9rem 2.25rem;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .btn-white:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }

    .cta-note { margin-top: 1.25rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }

    /* Footer */
    .footer { background: var(--ink); padding: 3rem 2rem; }

    .footer-inner {
      max-width: 1160px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .footer-logo img { height: 36px; width: auto; filter: brightness(0) invert(1); opacity: 0.85; }

    .footer-tagline {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    }

    .footer-right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end; gap: 0.5rem; }

    .footer-linkedin { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); transition: color 0.2s; }
    .footer-linkedin:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); }

    .footer-copy { font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3rem; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .hero-visual { order: -1; }
      .hero-logo-card { max-width: 100%; padding: 2.5rem; }
      .about-cs-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .conditions-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .section { padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero-headline { font-size: 2.1rem; }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .hero-headline .underline-word::after { animation: none; width: 100%; }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Google Analytics -->
<script is:inline async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-4Q4WLD7DGS"></script>
<script is:inline>
  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
  gtag('js', new Date());
  gtag('config', 'G-4Q4WLD7DGS');
</script>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="nav" role="navigation" aria-label="Main navigation">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo" aria-label="Connected Speech home">
        <img src="/connected-speech-logo-transparent.png" alt="Connected Speech logo" />
      </a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#about">About Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="#jodi">Meet Jodi</a></li>
        <li><a href="#conditions">What We Work On</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Get in Touch</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <span class="hero-eyebrow">Speech Therapy · Johannesburg</span>
        <h1 class="hero-headline" id="hero-heading">
          We give people the ability to <span class="underline-word">communicate their needs</span>.
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
          For some, that means a child saying <strong>"mom"</strong> or <strong>"dad"</strong> for the first time.
          For others, it means being understood at the dinner table, in the classroom, at work, or anywhere that matters.
          With words, with signs, with anything that works.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Book a Session</a>
          <a href="#about" class="btn-ghost">Learn more</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="hero-logo-card">
          <img src="/connected-speech-logo-transparent.png" alt="Connected Speech" />
          <p class="hero-logo-tagline">The day your child communicates what they need, and gets it.</br>That's what we work towards.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission Bar -->
    <div class="mission-bar" aria-label="Our mission">
      <p>Every child deserves to be heard. Every family deserves to be connected.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- About Connected Speech -->
    <section class="section about-cs" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="about-cs-grid">
          <div class="about-cs-text">
            <span class="section-label">Who We Are</span>
            <h2 class="section-heading" id="about-heading">Built on one belief — everyone thrives when communication is consistent.</h2>
            <div class="section-body">
              <p>
                Connected Speech is a Johannesburg-based speech therapy practice working with children and adults
                who face communication challenges. We work with those who stutter, with language delays,
                feeding difficulties, and with complex communication needs.
              </p>
              <p>
                Communication is more than speech. Some find their voice with words. Others use signs,
                symbols, devices, or gestures — and every one of those pathways is equally valid. Our job is to
                find what works for you and build on it, in every environment where you live, learn, and grow.
              </p>
              <p>
                That means therapy does not stop when the session ends. We bring consistent, goal-driven support
                into the spaces that matter most — so progress is not left at the door.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="values-list" aria-label="Our values">
              <div class="value-item">
                <div class="value-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <p><strong>Person-centred.</strong> Every therapy plan is built around the individual — their needs, their pace, their world.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="value-item">
                <div class="value-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <p><strong>Inclusive by design.</strong> Communication takes many forms. We support all of them.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="value-item">
                <div class="value-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <p><strong>Family-first.</strong> Families are partners in therapy, not bystanders. We make sure you know exactly how to support your loved one between sessions.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="value-item">
                <div class="value-dot" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                <p><strong>Results you can see.</strong> Real progress, reported clearly, after every session.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-cs-visual" aria-hidden="true">
            <img src="/connected-speech-logo-transparent.png" alt="" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Jodi -->
    <section class="section about-jodi" id="jodi" aria-labelledby="jodi-heading">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="about-jodi-grid">
          <div class="about-jodi-text">
            <span class="section-label">Meet the Founder</span>
            <h2 class="section-heading" id="jodi-heading">Jodi Zimmerman</h2>
            <div class="section-body">
              <p>
                Jodi has spent almost a decade working with people who communicate differently — and she has never
                tired of the moment someone finds a way to be understood.
              </p>
              <p>
                After four years embedded in a government school for children with autism, Jodi developed a deep
                understanding of what people are capable of when they are given the right tools, the right
                environment, and someone who truly believes in them. That experience shaped everything about how
                Connected Speech works today.
              </p>
              <p>
                Jodi specialises in Augmentative and Alternative Communication — AAC — working with those
                whose communication goes beyond speech. Makaton signing, the PROMPT, picture-based
                communication, and high-tech devices are all part of her toolkit. She builds individualised therapy
                plans for each person, because no two people communicate in exactly the same way.
              </p>
              <p>
                Her master's dissertation explored how youth empowerment programs can facilitate participation for
                young people with disabilities — research that continues to shape her approach to therapy and her
                belief that every person deserves a seat at the table.
              </p>
              <p>
                She was selected for the Dean's List during her master's program — a reflection of the same
                commitment she brings to every person she works with.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="jodi-credentials" aria-label="Jodi's qualifications">
              <div class="credential">
